responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1771C9794565D86B3114A2AF79D9E1E7", "You should know, I don\'t think Oakenbane Keep is a safe place to be right now. There\'s a conflict brewing. The Terrorgore Minotaur are gathering around a new leader, and if I\'m reading the signs right, that leader is about to attempt a ritual of banishment in the Keep. My guess is that they\'re trying to drive out the resident spirits.")
